# Disease.Zone - BlueBlocks Healthcare Intelligence Layer

## Status: LIVE
- https://disease.zone - Countdown to Feb 2, 2026
- https://api.disease.zone - API coming soon
- https://portal.disease.zone - Patient portal
- https://doctors.disease.zone - Provider portal

## BlueBlocks Ecosystem Architecture

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    BLUEBLOCKS ECOSYSTEM                     │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                                             │
│  ┌─────────────────┐         ┌─────────────────┐           │
│  │   BlueBlocks    │         │  Disease.Zone   │           │
│  │   (Layer 1)     │◄───────►│  (Intelligence) │           │
│  │                 │         │                 │           │
│  │ • Blockchain    │         │ • 138+ APIs     │           │
│  │ • Smart Contr.  │         │ • Outbreak Det. │           │
│  │ • Health IDs    │         │ • AI Symptoms   │           │
│  │ • BBT Tokens    │         │ • FHIR/Epic     │           │
│  │ • Provider Reg. │         │ • STI Tracking  │           │
│  └─────────────────┘         └─────────────────┘           │
│           │                           │                     │
│           └───────────┬───────────────┘                     │
│                       │                                     │
│              ┌────────▼────────┐                           │
│              │    Keycloak     │                           │
│              │    (SSO Auth)   │                           │
│              └─────────────────┘                           │
│                                                             │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

## Integration Points

### disease.zone APIs → BlueBlocks
- Global outbreak data → Blockchain audit logs
- Patient symptom analysis → Medical record contracts
- Provider verification → Provider registry contract
- Health tokens → BBT token rewards

### BlueBlocks → disease.zone
- Wallet authentication
- Medical record access
- Provider credentials
- Token-gated features

## Launch Timeline
- 2026-01-18: Countdown page live
- 2026-02-02: Full platform launch
- Q1 2026: Keycloak integration
- Q1 2026: BlueBlocks SDK integration
- Q2 2026: Doctor/Patient portals

